description: This file defines the interface for the WanManager in the RDKB components, including function prototypes related to message bus engagement and resource management.

methods.name: ssp_Mbi_MessageBusEngage
methods.description: Engages the message bus for the specified component using the provided configuration.

methods.name: ssp_Mbi_Initialize
methods.description: Initializes the message bus interface with user data.

methods.name: ssp_Mbi_Finalize
methods.description: Finalizes and cleans up resources for the message bus interface.

methods.name: ssp_Mbi_Buscheck
methods.description: Checks the status of the message bus.

methods.name: ssp_Mbi_FreeResources
methods.description: Frees resources based on priority and user data.
